      <title>阿根廷阻止银行在货币贬值前囤积美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/argentina-stops-banks-from-hoarding-dollars-ahead-of-devaluation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷央行限制了该国商业银行可以持有的外币数量，以阻止人们在当选总统哈维尔·米雷周日就职后预计贬值之前囤积美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/argentina-stops-banks-from-hoarding-dollars-ahead-of-devaluation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:26:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登弹劾调查将于下周众议院投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/biden-impeachment-inquiry-set-for-house-vote-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院共和党人周四迈出了一步，正式授权对总统乔·拜登进行与其家族商业交易有关的弹劾调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/biden-impeachment-inquiry-set-for-house-vote-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:23:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大要求石油和天然气公司减排高达 38%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/canada-to-require-oil-gas-emissions-cut-of-35-to-38-in-2030</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将要求其石油和天然气行业在六年内将排放量削减至比 2019 年水平低 35% 至 38%，政府称这对于主要化石燃料生产国来说是历史性的首次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/canada-to-require-oil-gas-emissions-cut-of-35-to-38-in-2030</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国不太可能在年底前完成修订后的预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/german-coalition-aiming-for-friday-deal-on-revised-2024-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳表示，他预计执政联盟将在“几天内”就修订后的 2024 年预算结构达成政治协议，同时承认该协议不太可能按计划在年底前获得议会通过。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/german-coalition-aiming-for-friday-deal-on-revised-2024-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 08:27:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据美联社报道，杀害三人的校园枪击案凶手是内华达大学拉斯维加斯分校的教授</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-07/vegas-shooter-who-killed-3-was-a-professor-who-recently-applied-for-a-job-at-unlv-ap-source-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉斯维加斯（美联社）——当一名枪手在内华达大学拉斯维加斯分校大楼的地板上徘徊时，惊恐的学生和教授们躲在教室和宿舍里，造成三人死亡，第四人重伤，然后在与警方的枪战中死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-07/vegas-shooter-who-killed-3-was-a-professor-who-recently-applied-for-a-job-at-unlv-ap-source-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 05:30:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉不情愿地成为委内瑞拉-圭亚那危机的调解人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/lula-reluctantly-adopts-mediator-role-in-venezuela-guyana-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期以来，巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦一直试图将自己定位为全球冲突的独立仲裁者，现在面临着调解巴西北部邻国委内瑞拉和圭亚那之间危机的艰巨任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/lula-reluctantly-adopts-mediator-role-in-venezuela-guyana-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 03:44:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
